{"tid":2094350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃文萱議辦開張  警方到場要求移除旗幟否則拘捕","createTime":"2020-07-04T14:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T15:05:09.000Z","uid":7542,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"54b054901555006f2656872d037151f8b0c5efab","tid":2094350,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:34:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">社會各界到場慶祝新辦事處開張，包括警方 </span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沙田區議員黃文萱位於沙田第一城的議員辦事處，今天下午開張，一批警員到場，指辦事處內一幅「光復香港時代革命」旗幟有分裂國家或者顛覆國家政權的意圖，會觸犯《港區國安法》，要求她們移除，否則可能會發出拘捕令。政府日前發聲明，指「光復香港時代革命」有「港獨」或者顛覆國家政權的含意，律政司司長鄭若驊說，政府無因為實施《港區國安法》而改變對這八個字的解釋，希望市民不要以身試法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535823-20200704.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535823-20200704.htm&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmlznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=7a5bc1dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535823-20200704.htm&h=7520cc4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535823-20200704.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gwl0TLLfRcw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fgwl0TLLfRcw&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmlznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=0bac68ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gwl0TLLfRcw</a>"},{"pid":"a1ab5627ca2e6cb1e1eedcc3c3eaf03ad2642468","tid":2094350,"uid":66221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"新民黨光頭佬趕住奶閪門梓袋底唔霸住個辦事處啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9405418794f793f41b5bf251cca1e83c37f064","tid":2094350,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:59:59.000Z","msg":"只會影響一小部分人～"},{"pid":"91a8733db5033efb6599ebeca891d4b6236b7615","tid":2094350,"uid":32534